    a <http://schema.theodi.org/odrs#RightsStatement>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#d68d2f3f93f0cb3f1abe12fb0e392396>.
<#d68d2f3f93f0cb3f1abe12fb0e392396> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/76fd0da7-1e91-4ad3-a88b-8c2f89b0b2e0>;
