<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#de29470e3d188b92a3d2368812f6ed0a>.
<#de29470e3d188b92a3d2368812f6ed0a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/5725fbd4c56dab0587f30b0624256078>;
