<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#780e27bc720cc4131e3e67d18d058924>.
<#780e27bc720cc4131e3e67d18d058924> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://statistikdatabasen.scb.se/dataset/TAB3584>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-22T06:17:53.328Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#780e27bc720cc4131e3e67d18d058924> {
<https://statistikdatabasen.scb.se/dataset/TAB3584> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Energi"@sv, "Energy"@en, "Old tables, not updated"@en, "Elpriser och elavtal"@sv, "Electricity prices and electricity contracts"@en, "Äldre tabeller, uppdateras ej"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/MONTHLY>;
