<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#b59e3ec9ba7d1f4b32a1a11ff3d425df>.
<#b59e3ec9ba7d1f4b32a1a11ff3d425df> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
